race.comment: ANALYZATION (7) is a promising type who notched his 9th career success when too good (25.09) at this track last time. Hard to go past form here, unbeaten in two starts. Was a winner at his only start from this draw. Great chance to get the job done again. BAROOGA JIM (1) goes very well at the course and distance with two wins and a placing from three starts. In the money last time at Ballarat (25.65) in a Grade 5, finishing a 5 length third. Looks suited here and can measure up. ELITE ONE (2) recorded a win over 390m at Ballarat in a blistering 22.08 last start. Harder here but will be in this for a long way. STAR REBEL (5) comes into calculations after placing most recently.
